				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="084d75b8-b80b-4232-bb76-7c0abe9c4b93" >

    <h3>Step 2</h3> 
<p>For those events that carry a severity of risk level from 2 to 4 (minor to major), evaluate all the control measures that will be taken to reduce the likelihood of the risk (may cause minor injuries, severe injuries or disaster/death). With all control measures in place, use reasonable judgement to determine the likelihood of the risk occurring (ranging from 1 to 4).</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#084d75b8-b80b-4232-bb76-7c0abe9c4b93");});</script></div>

				

				
				<div class="resTable parbase section">























 



	<div class="scrollIndicator hidden">
		<i class="fa fa-long-arrow-left" aria-hidden="true"></i> Swipe to see more <i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
	</div>
	<div id="e1aff3b7-808e-4a58-959e-941fb2667060">
		<table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1" border="1">
<tbody><tr><td width="15%"><p><strong>Rating</strong></p>
</td>
<td><p><strong>Likelihood level of the risk occurring&nbsp;</strong></p>
</td>
</tr><tr><td><p><strong>1</strong></p>
</td>
<td><p><strong>Rare</strong>: There is a low probability of the hazard to occur</p>
</td>
</tr><tr><td><p><strong>2</strong></p>
</td>
<td><p><strong>Possible</strong>: Hazard may occur at some time</p>
</td>
</tr><tr><td><p><strong>3</strong></p>
</td>
<td><p><strong>Likely</strong>: A hazard will probably occur in most circumstances</p>
</td>
</tr><tr><td><p><strong>4</strong></p>
</td>
<td><p><strong>Almost</strong>&nbsp;<strong>certain</strong>: A hazard can be expected</p>
</td>
</tr></tbody></table>

	</div>




