<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="c81093f5-24fb-4960-8705-f0ff9aef8450" >

    <h3>Step 3</h3> 
<p>Multiply the severity level (S) with the likelihood (L) to receive the risk level (RL). Identify the risk level based on the risk assessment matrix (S x L = RL).</p> 
<h4>Risk assessment matrix</h4>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#c81093f5-24fb-4960-8705-f0ff9aef8450");});</script></div>

				

				
