<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="72382ee2-b959-4f51-940b-7f39782edeae" >

    <ul> 
 <li>Participants working directly with or near chemicals (handling, storing and disposing): <a href="/content/ryerson/facilities-management-development/environmental-health-safety/laboratory-safety/chemical-safety.html">Chemical Safety eLearning module in D2L</a>.</li> 
 <li>Participants working with computers, laptops or tools (data entry): <a href="/content/ryerson/facilities-management-development/environmental-health-safety/ergonomics.html">Office Ergonomics eLearning module in D2L </a>.</li> 
 <li>Participants working at a construction site or working at heights: <a href="/content/ryerson/facilities-management-development/environmental-health-safety/hazards-at-work/working-at-heights.html">Working at Heights training</a>.</li> 
 <li>Participants <a href="/content/ryerson/facilities-management-development/environmental-health-safety/hazards-at-work/transportation-dangerous-goods.html">transporting dangerous goods or products</a>: Contact Environmental Health and Safety at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:ehs@ryerson.ca">ehs@ryerson.ca</a> or 416-979-5000, ext. 553770 to schedule a training session.&nbsp;</li> 
 <li>Participants working with X-rays: Download the training slides on the <a href="/content/ryerson/facilities-management-development/environmental-health-safety/laboratory-safety/x-ray-safety.html">X-ray Safety page</a> and contact EHS to complete the quiz.</li> 
 <li>Participants handling <a href="/content/ryerson/facilities-management-development/environmental-health-safety/laboratory-safety/laser-safety.html">lasers</a>: Contact Environmental Health and Safety at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:ehs@ryerson.ca">ehs@ryerson.ca</a> or 416-979-5000, ext. 553770 to schedule a training session.&nbsp;</li> 
 <li>Participants working with biological agents: Download the training slides on the <a href="/content/ryerson/facilities-management-development/environmental-health-safety/laboratory-safety/biological-safety.html">Biological Safety page</a> and contact EHS to complete the quiz.</li> 
 <li>Participants working with radioactive materials: Contact Environmental Health and Safety at <a href="mailto:ehs@ryerson.ca">ehs@ryerson.ca</a> or 416-979-5000, ext. 553770 to schedule a training session.&nbsp;</li> 
</ul>
    





